%3D%5C%229ea47a1e-4dd8-4784-b759-b9d084990d12%5C%22%3EThe%20long-term%20effects%20of%20heat%20stroke%20can%20be%20debilitating%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amy%20Steel%20feeds%20a%20baby%20kangroo%20from%20a%20bottle%20in%20a%20bag%20around%20her%20neck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccca151aa2ac29ee34606d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22876%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEight%20years%20after%20getting%20heat%20stroke%2C%20Amy%20Steel%20is%20still%20dealing%20with%20its%20effects.%3Cp%3ELewis%20Blaustein%2FEcoAthletes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlexander%20said%20restricted%20blood%20flow%20to%20the%20gut%20during%20heat%20stroke%20can%20release%20bacteria%20into%20the%20bloodstream.%20This%20can%20cause%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcytokine-storm-severe-coronavirus-case-death-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecytokine%20storm%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20way%20some%20people's%20immune%20systems%20overreact%20to%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20see%20this%20really%20huge%20response%20of%20the%20immune%20system%20to%20severe%20heat-related%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20This%20kind%20of%20overreaction%20can%20trigger%20a%20series%20of%20other%20illnesses%20long%20after%20a%20heat%20stroke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20collapse%20and%20hospitalization%2C%20Steel%2C%20for%20example%2C%20developed%20tonsilitis%20though%20she'd%20had%20her%20tonsils%20removed.%20A%20bout%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmono-shot-possible-cure-ms-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglandular%20fever%3C%2Fa%3E%20she'd%20had%20in%20childhood%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adelaidenow.com.au%2Fsport%2Fnetball%2Fthunderbirds-defender-amy-steel-sidelined-for-at-least-a-month-of-anz-championship%2Fnews-story%2F64ee5457170c030f5b132c0abc98e79c%5C%22%20target