D%5C%22Dating%20app%20advertisement%20for%20Friend%20of%20a%20Friend%20on%20a%20telephone%20pole%20that%20reads%20%26quot%3BYour%20Single%20Friends%20Need%20This%26quot%3B%20in%20SoHo%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cc9a8a1aa2ac29ee3417ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222075%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnushka%20Joshi's%20dating%20app%20Friend%20of%20a%20Friend%20has%20ads%20plastered%20around%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3ESydney%20Bradley%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20New%20York%20City%2C%20two%20healthcare%20workers%20who%20had%20never%20started%20a%20business%20are%20diving%20headfirst%20into%20reimagining%20the%20double%20date.%20In%20Paris%2C%20a%20woman%20who%20worked%20for%20Microsoft%20leveraged%20decades%20of%20experience%20in%20tech%20to%20create%20a%20digital%20map%20of%20missed%20connections.%20And%20on%20Instagram%2C%20influencer%20Serena%20Kerrigan%20took%20matters%20into%20her%20own%20hands%20by%20letting%20followers%20shoot%20their%20shots%20in%20a%20mass%20group%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20scare%20the%20shit%20out%20of%20Hinge%20and%20Bumble%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kerrigan%2C%20who%20has%20about%20800%2C000%20followers%20across%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20really%20disrupt%20the%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%2C%20too%2C%20are%20paying%20attention.%20Rex%20Woodbury%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Daybreak%20Ventures%2C%20told%20BI%20earlier%20this%20summer%20that%20internet%20dating%20companies%20were%20%26quot%3Bvery%20disruptable%20in%20this%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20founders%20of%2011%20startups%20who%20believe%20they%20have%20the%20next%20great%20innovation%20in%20dating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a11352ba-4f1d-49bd-b6ea-654d71b42c85%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20anti-swipe%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20anti-swipers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20setting%20out%20to%20build%20a%20dating%20app%2C%20swiping%20fatigue%20was%20top%20of%20mind%20for%20%3Cstrong%3EPique%20Dating%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efounders%20Vaish%20Sesetty%20and%20Cyrus%20Belsoi.%20The%20two%20previously%20worked%20at%20AWS%20and%20Datadog%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vaish%20Sesetty%20and%20Cyrus%20Belsoi%20founded%20Pique%20Dating%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cc9c32c72ebc54a40ebeb8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVaish%20Sesetty%20and%20Cyrus%20Belsoi%20cofounded%20Pique%20Dating.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Pique%20Dating%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20trying%20to%20get%20people%20to%20actually%20see%20people%20as%20people%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Belsoi%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pique%20app%2C%20which%20provides%20people%20with%20up%20to%20six%20matches%20per%20day%20after%20a%20user%20answers%20a%20multiple-choice%20question%2C%20has%20no%20swiping%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20its%20low-tech%20app%2C%20Pique%20Dating%20also%20hosts%20in-person%20events%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20The%20founders%20host%20speed-dating%20parties%20where%20people%20answer%20a%20single%20question%20before%20the%20event%20begins%2C%20and%20on%20weekends%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20they%20host%20a%20pop-up%20in%20McCarren%20Park%20where%20park-goers%20can%20snap%20a%20picture%20in%20real%20time%2C%20write%20out%20a%20bio%2C%20and%20passersby%20can%20inquire%20about%20the%20singles%20posted%20on%20the%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20France%2C%20tech%20professional%20Karima%20Ben%20Abdelmalek%2C%20with%20a%20background%20in%20Microsoft%20and%20Dailymotion%2C%20felt%20that%20dating%20apps%20needed%20a%20more%20social%20element%20as%20far%20back%20as%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbdelmalek%20created%20%3Cstrong%3EHappn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20where%20users%20turn%20on%20their%20location%20and%20are%20notified%20when%20they've%20bumped%20into%20another%20Happn%20user%20while%20going%20about%20their%20day-to-day%20lives.%20The%20hope%20is%20that%20you%20meet%20like-minded%20singles%20in%20the%20places%20you%20already%20frequent%20%E2%80%94%20bars%2C%20restaurants%2C%20and%20concerts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSingles%20today%20are%20looking%20to%20bring%20back%20real-life%20encounters%2C%20like%20going%20to%20bars%20and%20restaurants%2C%26quot%3B%20Abdelmalek%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BOur%20mission%20today%20is%20to%20bring%20back%20people%20meeting%20offline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Happn%20launched%20nearly%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20the%20app%20was%20ahead%20of%20its%20time%20in%20terms%20of%20prioritizing%20in-person%20connection%20over%20swiping%20and%20DMing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20startups%2C%20like%20%3Cstrong%3EFirst%20Round's%20on%20Me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20are%20prioritizing%20in-app%20actions%20that%20direct%20users%20to%20set%20up%20a%20date%20instead%20of%20endlessly%20swiping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20easy%20to%20swipe%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20like%20a%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20FROM's%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Joe%20Feminella%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20you're%20playing%20Tetris%20or%20something%2C%20and%20that's%20kind%20of%20what%20dehumanized%20it%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joe%20Feminella%20CEO%20of%20First%20Round's%20on%20Me%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccd02a43b5e59d16b55f93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221410%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoe%20Feminella%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20First%20Round's%20on%20Me.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20FROM%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFROM%2C%20which%20Feminella%20cofounded%20with%20his%20wife%20Hannah%20(who%20not-so-ironically%20met%20through%20Hinge)%2C%20encourages%20users%20to%20%26quot%3Bgo%20on%20a%20date%26quot%3B%20and%20get%20out%20into%20the%20world.%20While%20the%20app%20does%20have%20a%20stack%20of%20potential%20matches%20on%20its%20app%20that%20users%20can%20click%20through%2C%20there%20is%20no%20swipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20FROM%20announced%20it%20raised%20%243%20million%20in%20seed%20funding%20from%20family-run%20fund%20Manna%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e6ea7f9-598f-4bf4-8e2d-a84eda258fd9%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20'we%20met%20through%20friends'%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20we-met-through-friends%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20the%20matchmakers%20are%20the%20friends%20we%20make%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElle%20Wilson%2C%20dating%20coach%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20NYC-based%20dating%20event%20series%3Cstrong%3E%20Met%20Through%20Friends%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20was%20planning%20dinner%20parties%20for%20her%20friends%20in%202022.%20Like%20many%2020-something-year-olds%2C%20Wilson's%20friends%20often%20complained%20about%20the%20trials%20and%20tribulations%20of%20dating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20things%20feel%20really%20challenging%20for%20people%20who%20are%20dating%20and%20people%20who%20are%20single%20and%20don't%20want%20to%20be%2C%20but%20I%20know%20they%20know%20lots%20of%20great%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20we%20got%20them%20all%20in%20a%20room%20together%20and%20saw%20what%20happened%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222107%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elle%20Wilson%20headshot%20wearing%20black%20shirt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cc9d3fc72ebc54a40ebf90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221580%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElle%20Wilson%20launched%20Met%20Through%20Friends%20in%202024.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Elle%20Wilson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20events%2C%20which%20now%20bring%20together%20about%20300%20attendees%20each%20month%2C%20require%20people%20to%20bring%20a%20friend%20with%20them%20%E2%80%94%20a%20built-in%20wingman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDating%20with%20friends%20is%20also%20the%20premise%20of%20%3Cstrong%3EFourplay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20believes%20the%20future%20of%20dating%20is%20double%20or%20nothing.%20Singles%20make%20joint%20profiles%20with%20their%20friends%20and%20match%20with%20other%20duos%2C%20but%20founders%20Danielle%20Dietzek%20and%20Julie%20Griggs%20don't%20see%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20date%26quot%3B%20as%20exclusively%20a%20pairing-off%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221090%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fourplay%20founders%20Danielle%20Dietzek%20and%20Julie%20Griggs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccac561aa2ac29ee34280e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22818%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDanielle%20Dietzek%20and%20Julie%20Griggs%20founded%20Fourplay%20in%202019.%3Cp%3ENicole%20Fara%20Silver%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20really%20are%20no%20expectations%20with%20Fourplay%2C%26quot%3B%20Dietzek%20said.%20Instead%2C%20the%20founders%20see%20Fourplay%20as%20an%20invitation%20for%20a%20friendship%2C%20a%20relationship%2C%20or%20simply%20a%20fun%20night%20out.%20The%20point%20is%20to%20make%20meeting%20new%20people%20less%20stressful%20and%20less%20lonely%20simply%20by%20doing%20it%20with%20a%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20doing%20something%20together%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20being%20isolated%20on%20their%20own%20devices%20and%20going%20at%20singlehood%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20Dietzek%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20sometimes%20your%20friends%20can't%20be%20there%20on%20your%20first%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnushka%20Joshi%2C%20founder%20of%20%3Cstrong%3EFriend%20of%20a%20Friend%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20launching%20a%20dating%20app%20focused%20on%20mutual%20connections%20to%20make%20dating%20less%20daunting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDating%20is%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20decisions%20or%20activities%20that%20we%20do%20in%20our%2020s%20and%20beyond%2C%26quot%3B%20Joshi%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20friends%20and%20I%20were%20just%20coming%20up%20against%20a%20lot%20of%20problems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20from%20post-pandemic%20awkwardness%20to%20dating%20apps%20growing%20into%20colossal%20businesses%20%26quot%3Bmade%20it%20hard%20for%20us%20to%20date%2C%26quot%3B%20Joshi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20meeting%20someone%20through%20a%20friend%20felt%20more%20natural.%20In%20fact%2C%20it's%20how%20Hinge%20originally%20made%20its%20pitch%20to%20new%20users%20in%202014.%20Feeling%20that%20the%20dating%20app%20market%20had%20abandoned%20this%20form%20of%20connection%2C%20Joshi%20started%20building%20Friend%20of%20a%20Friend%20earlier%20this%20year%20and%20plans%20to%20launch%20an%20app%20in%20the%20fall.%20Users%20will%20share%20their%20contact%20book%20data%20with%20the%20app%20and%20be%20able%20to%20see%20how%20many%20mutual%20connections%20they%20share%20with%20other%20users%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anushka%20Joshi%20headshot%20sitting%20in%20front%20of%20a%20fireplace%20with%20magazines.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cc9d981aa2ac29ee341a4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnushka%20Joshi%20founded%20Friend%20of%20a%20Friend%20in%202024.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Anushka%20Joshi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20it's%20naive%20or%20hopeful%20of%20me%2C%20but%20I%20just%20want%20people%20to%20have%20an%20experience%20on%20the%20app%20where%20it's%20like%2C%20'I'm%20really%20meeting%20someone%20that%20I%20connect%20with'%20instead%20of%20feeling%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20that%20was%20just%20another%20shitty%20date%20%5Bwith%5D%20another%20stranger%2C'%26quot%3B%20Joshi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba20e818-1fd3-4913-9403-7af61ee20faf%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20more-than-just-pictures%20crowd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20more-than-just-pictures%20crowd%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoo%20Dating%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20founder%20Derek%20Lee%20wants%20personality%20to%20shine%20through%20the%20small%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20dating%20moved%20online%2C%20it%20created%20a%20ton%20of%20winners%20and%20losers%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20told%20BI.%20Picture-first%20profiles%20drove%20users%20to%20care%20more%20about%20looks%20than%20the%20potential%20real-life%20chemistry%20two%20users%20might%20have%2C%20Lee%20believes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20his%20two%20cofounders%2C%20Lee%20designed%20Boo%20to%20%26quot%3Bjailbreak%20the%20swiping%20mode%26quot%3B%20by%20allowing%20users%20to%20share%20memes%2C%20art%2C%20poetry%2C%20and%20geek%20out%20on%20their%20interests%20with%20other%20uses%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20building%20a%20perfectly%20manicured%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222452%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Boo%20Dating%20David%20Chang%20(26)%2C%20Derek%20Lee%20(30)%2C%20Richard%20Chang%20(31)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccab7b43b5e59d16b522fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221612%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBoo%20Dating%20cofounders%3A%20David%20Chang%2C%20Derek%20Lee%2C%20and%20Richard%20Chang.%20%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Boo%20Dating%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHashtag%20%26quot%3Buniverses%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20topics%20like%20%23fashion%20and%20%23outdoors%2C%20are%20central%20to%20the%20Boo%20experience%2C%20where%20users%20can%20meet%20like-minded%20matches.%20Boo%20users%20still%20create%20profiles%20and%20swipe%2C%20however%2C%20but%20are%20shown%20compatible%20profiles%20partially%20based%20on%20an%20MBTI-like%20personality%20quiz%20they%20take%20when%20they%20register.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20just%20waiting%20for%20a%20swipe%20back%2C%20you%20can%20engage%2C%20have%20fun%2C%20tell%20jokes%2C%20and%20share%20memes%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20much%20more%20dynamic%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENYC%20lawyer%20Katya%20Chernyak%20was%20likewise%20disillusioned%20by%20the%20gap%20between%20stunning%20profiles%20online%20and%20lackluster%20in-person%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20wasting%20so%20much%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Chernyak%20recalled%20to%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20an%20honest%20platform%20where%20you%20could%20experience%20that%20person%20right%20off%20the%20bat%2C%20which%20would%20lead%20to%20higher%20quality%20matches.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Chernyak%20followed%20her%20frustration%20out%20of%20her%20legal%20career%20and%2C%20along%20with%20two%20cofounders%2C%20launched%20the%20video-profile%20dating%20app%3Cstrong%3E%20FFWD.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Looking%20directly%20into%20the%20camera%2C%20users%20answer%20five%20question%20prompts%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20expensive%2C%20but%20worth%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BWhat%20would%20your%20friends%20say%20is%20your%20best%20quality%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFFWD%20allows%20users%20as%20many%20takes%20as%20they%20need%2C%20but%20bans%20any%20quick%20edits%20or%20filters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22FFWD%20Katya%20Chernyak%20(32)%20Aeen%20Avini%20(43)%20Victoria%20Todis%20(50)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccabbe1aa2ac29ee3427b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFFWD%20cofunders%20Katya%20Chernyak%2C%20Aeen%20Avini%2C%20and%20Victoria%20Todis.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20FFWD%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20expanding%20out%20of%20NYC%20to%20Chicago%2C%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20and%20Phoenix%2C%20the%20next%20frontier%20for%20FFWD%20is%20an%20algorithm%20that%20understands%20the%20nuances%20of%20capturing%20personality%20on%20video%2C%20like%2