ble%20to%20slide%20into%20someone's%20DM%2C%20which%20feels%20more%20intentional%20and%20approachable%20than%20a%20swipe%20on%20a%20Hinge%20or%20a%20Bumble%2C%26quot%3B%20Kerrigan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20running%20the%20Instagram-based%20dating%20channel%2C%20Kerrigan%20also%20sells%20a%20dating%20card%20game%20with%20conversation%20prompts%2C%20also%20called%20%26quot%3BLet's%20Fucking%20Date.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2218d8137f-17a8-44ae-a5cc-ba60e7ca5220%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20dating%20coaches%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20dating%20coaches%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20finding%20a%20new%20match%2C%20some%20dating%20startups%20are%20trying%20to%20help%20people%20navigate%20the%20various%20stages%20of%20dating%20with%20coaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20this%20huge%20gap%20in%20the%20market%20around%2C%20weirdly%20enough%2C%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nandini%20Mullaji%2C%20matchmaker%20and%20founder%20of%20AI-powered%20dating%20coaching%20app%20%3Cstrong%3ESitch%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMullaji%2C%20who%20herself%20is%20happily%20married%2C%20has%20been%20setting%20people%20up%20on%20dates%20in%202024%20by%20collecting%20information%20through%20a%20form%20she'd%20shared%20with%20her%20Substack%2C%20Instagram%2C%20and%20TikTok%20followers.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20goal%20to%20set%20up%2050%20dates%20snowballed%20into%20setting%20up%20more%20than%20200%20people%2C%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222178%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nandini%20Mullaji%20headshot%20wearing%20denim%20jacket%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cc9ed31aa2ac29ee341b7b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221634%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENandini%20Mullaji%20founded%20Sitch%20in%202024.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Nandini%20Mullaji%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20now%20building%20a%20new%20app%20called%20Sitch%20to%20help%20people%20navigate%20the%20dating%20process%20using%20AI%2C%20which%20she%20trained%20to%20replicate%20the%20flow%20of%20conversation%20one%20would%20have%20with%20a%20professional%20matchmaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20put%20in%20screenshots%2C%20you%20can%20put%20in%20your%20dating%20app%20profile%2C%20you%20can%20put%20in%20other%20people's%20dating%20app%20profiles%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20the%20opening%20line%20should%20be%2C%20all%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Mullaji%20said.%20On%20top%20of%20coaching%2C%20the%20app%20will%20also%20include%20a%20matchmaking%20product%20that%20will%20introduce%20users%20to%20a%20handful%20of%20potential%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%2C%20which%20will%20launch%20in%20September%20as%20invite-only%2C%20already%20has%20over%207%2C000%20members%20on%20the%20waitlist%2C%20per%20Mullaji.%20She%20secured%20a%20%241%20million%20angel%20investment%20from%20Lightspeed's%20Jeremy%20Lieu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESitch%20isn't%20the%20only%20AI-powered%20dating%20coach%20platform%20to%20gain%20the%20attention%20of%20prominent%20VCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmori%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20founded%20by%20Alex%20Weitzman%2C%20is%20backed%20by%20Daybreak%20Ventures'%20Rex%20Woodbury%20(the%20size%20of%20the%20investment%20has%20not%20been%20disclosed).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeitzman%20went%20viral%20on%20TikTok%20in%202023%20for%20a%20website%20she%20built%20where%20people%20could%20upload%20texts%20between%20themselves%20and%20their%20ex%2C%20analyze%20them%20using%20AI%2C%20and%2C%20as%20Weitzman%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Bfigure%20out%20what's%20wrong%20with%20you.%26quot%3B%20The%20cheeky%20website%20inspired%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20broader%20AI-powered%20dating%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221792%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alex%20Weitzman%20headshot%2C%20founder%20of%20Amori%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cc9ec11aa2ac29ee341b6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221344%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlex%20Weitzman%20founded%20Amori%20in%202023.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alex%20Weitzman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20sign%20up%20and%20fill%20out%20a%20questionnaire%20about%20their%20dating%20profiles%2C%20gender%2C%20identity%2C%20preferences%2C%20and%20dating%20goals%20to%20give%20the%20AI%20bots%20more%20context.%20The%20app%20has%20several%20dating%20coaches%20with%20distinct%20characteristics%2C%20like%20Tabitha%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bwise%20aunt%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20Ethan%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20wingman.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eddb7e1c-56c9-4621-896b-62d9a9087944%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20a%20recap%20of%20the%20startups%20disrupting%20the%20dating%20ecosystem%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmori%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20an%20AI-powered%20dating%20coach%20app%20where%20users%20can%20upload%20texts%20or%20screenshots%20to%20get%20advice%20about%20dating.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoo%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20a%20personality-driven%20app%20where%20users%20fill%20out%20quizzes%20and%20join%20threads%20based%20on%20mutual%20interests.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFourplay%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eallows%20friends%20to%20create%20joint%20profiles%20and%20match%20with%20other%20duos%20leading%20to%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20dates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFFWD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20a%20video-profile%20dating%20app%20where%20users%20answer%20five%20questions%20on-camera%20with%20no%20edits%20or%20filters.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%20Round's%20on%20Me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20a%20dating%20app%20that%20prioritizes%20making%20plans%20for%20a%20date.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFriend%20of%20a%20Friend%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20a%20dating%20app%20that%20connects%20mutual%20friends.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHappn%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20a%20location-based%20app%20where%20users%20meet%20connections%20they've%20come%20across%20in%20real%20life.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet's