0a%20shaker%20cup%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8e1081aa2ac29ee33d5e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECreatine%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20researched%20fitness%20supplements%20on%20the%20market.%20it%20offers%20a%20lot%20of%20value%20for%20its%20low%20costs%2C%20according%20to%20trainers%20and%20sports%20nutritionists.%3Cp%3EFarion_O%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20even%20more%20evidence%20that%20creatine%20may%20be%20the%20best-value%20fitness%20supplement%20you%20can%20buy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStudies%20suggest%20it%20can%20help%20you%20build%20muscle%2C%20burn%20fat%2C%20boost%20performance%2C%20and%20even%20protect%20your%20brain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20creatine%20is%20relatively%20cheap%20and%20considered%20safe%2C%20no%20supplement%20can%20replace%20overall%20health%20habits.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20going%20to%20buy%20one%20supplement%20for%20better%20gains%2C%20efficient%20fat%20loss%2C%20and%20improved%20overall%20health%2C%20growing%20evidence%20points%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreatine-supplements-build-muscle-how-to-use-expert-advice-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreatine%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20best%20bang%20for%20your%20buck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong%20a%20staple%20of%20the%20sports%20world%20and%20bodybuilding%20community%20alike%2C%20creatine%20is%20an%20combo%20of%20amino%20acids%20that%20provides%20energy%20to%20muscles.%20Our%20bodies%20naturally%20produce%20some%20creatine%2C%20and%20we%20can%20also%20get%20a%20bit%20of%20creatine%20in%20some%20foods%20like%20meat%20and%20fish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20researched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupplements-weight-loss-muscle-gain-should-you-use-for-fitness-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efitness%20supplements%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20study%20after%20study%20suggests%20it%20can%20offer%20a%20boost%20to%20performance%2C%20more%20strength%20and%20muscle%20gains%2C%20and%20even%20a%20healthier%20brain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreatine%20isn't%20new%20%E2%80%94%20it%20caught%20on%20as%20a%20supplement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3963244%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20the%2090s%3C%2Fa%3E%20thanks%20to%20Olympians%20who%20swore%20by%20it%20for%20elite%20athletic%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreatine-muscle-building-supplement-shortage-price-hikes-may-continue-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemand%20has%20exploded%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20and%20it's%20considered%20such%20as%20staple%20that%20gym%20buffs%20were%20willing%20to%20pay%20double%20the%20price%20during%20shortages%20post-pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20just%20consumers%3B%20scientists%20agree.%20This%20summer%2C%20even%20more%20science%20emerged%2C%20backing%20up%20the%20benefits%20of%20creatine%20for%20building%20muscle%20and%20burning%20fat%2C%20and%20side%20effects%20are%20minimal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20the%20evidence%20stacking%20up%2C%20and%20creatine's%20relatively%20low%20price%20point%2C%20experts%20consistently%20recommend%20it%20as%20a%20go-to%20supplement%20in%20the%20gym.%20Here's%20why%20you%20might%20want%20to%20try%20it%20(if%20you%20haven't%20already).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2249f121f4-2c03-46b3-9e43-6fd61ace0106%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreatine%20helps%20fuel%20more%20reps%2C%20leading%20to%20better%20gains%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20findings%20on%20creatine%20suggest%20it%20has%20a%20modest%20benefit%20for%20both%20muscle%20building%20and%20fat%20loss%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20published%20July%2023%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F39074168%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Journal%20of%20Strength%20and%20Conditioning%20Research%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20from%20the%20University%20of%20New%20South%20Wales%20concluded%20from%20existing%20data%20that%20creatine%20users%20get%20an%20extra%202.4%20pounds%20of%20lean%20muscle%2C%20and%20lose%20nearly%201.5%20pounds%20more%20fat%2C%20than%20people%20who%20don't%20supplement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExtensive%20previous%20research%20backs%20up%20the%20finding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fwhat-are-the-benefits-of-creatine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreatine%20is%20linked%20to%20benefits%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%2C%20while%20small%2C%20can%20be%20significant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20works%20by%20providing%20extra%20fuel%20to%20muscle%20tissue%2C%20powering%20more%20work%20in%20the%20gym%20for%20better%20gains%2C%20or%20faster%20fat%20burning%2C%20and%20can%20is%20also%20stored%20in%20the%20brain%20to%20protect%20cognitive%20health%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC8912287%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20research%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20other%20top%20fitness%20supplements%20have%20more%20mixed%20evidence%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20building%20muscle%20and%20burning%20fat.%20They%20may%20be%20useful%2C%20but%20in%20specific%20contexts%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fpre-workout%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPreworkouts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eare%20hugely%20popular.%20Scientists%20warn%20that%20they%20vary%20widely%20in%20ingredients.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-supplements-herbs-dangerous-2017-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProprietary%20blends%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20don't%20disclose%20what%20you're%20actually%20getting%2C%20and%20re