pplies%20bins%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccb8fec72ebc54a40edc53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20found%20a%20lot%20of%20school%20supplies%20for%20cheap%20prices%20at%20Target.%20%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Target%2C%20the%20back-to-school%20inventory%20was%20greatly%20reduced%2C%20but%20I%20still%20saw%20plenty%20of%20essential%20items%2C%20all%20marked%20at%2050%25%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20PaperMate%20pencils%20to%20Elmer's%20glue%2C%20I%20found%20many%20reliable%2C%20tried-and-true%20brands%20available%20to%20stock%20up%20on%20at%20an%20impressive%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PaperMate%20mechanical%20pencils%2C%20for%20example%2C%20retail%20for%20just%20under%20%2410%2C%20but%20were%20only%20%245%20as%20part%20of%20the%20half-off%20sale.%20I%20found%204-ounce%20bottles%20of%20Elmer's%20glue%20that%20are%20usually%20%241%20but%20were%20marked%20down%20to%2050%20cents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20local%20Walmart's%20back-to-school%20section%20had%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20been%20set%20up%20for%20Halloween.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Walmart%20Halloween%20section%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccb8fec72ebc54a40edc55%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20was%20nice%20to%20see%20Halloween%20stuff%20out%20but%20I%20wished%20Walmart%20had%20more%20discounted%20school%20supplies.%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20was%20in%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhalloween-fall-decor-shopping-review-michaels-vs-hobby-lobby-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efall%20mode%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20sections%20of%20the%20store%20that%20were%20back-to-school%20themed%20just%20last%20week%20were%20already%20filled%20with