ened%20up%20a%20lot%20more%20positive%20forces%20for%20the%20stock%20market%20that%20just%20haven't%20been%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Paulsen%2C%20who%20writes%20the%20Paulsen%20Perspectives%20newsletter%20after%20retiring%20from%20a%2040-year%20career%20on%20Wall%20Street%20in%202022%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20only%20bull%20market%20in%20post-war%20history%20where%20the%20Fed%20has%20been%20tight%20throughout%20its%20entire%20existence.%20Normally%2C%20the%20Fed%20is%20easing%20before%20the%20bull%20even%20starts.%20So%20in%20some%20way%2C%20I%20think%20the%20Fed%20in%20doing%20this%2C%20is%20taking%20us%20back%20to%20the%20start%20of%20the%20bull.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20positive%20forces%20unlocked%20by%20the%20Fed%20include%20falling%20interest%20rates%20and%20bond%20yields%20and%20accelerating%20monetary%20growth%2C%20all%20of%20which%20have%20been%20absent%20for%20the%20current%20bull%20market%20that%20began%20in%20October%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20forces%2C%20combined%20with%20positive%20real%20GDP%20growth%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-consumer-price-index-in-july-fed-interest-rates-2024-8%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520consumer%2520price%2520index%2520increased%2Clower%2520than%2520June%2527s%25203.0%2525%2520read.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtinued%20disinflation%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20improve%20the%20mood%20among%20business%20owners%20and%20consumers%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20put%20all%20these%20together%2C%20something%20we%20haven't%20had%20at%20all%20yet%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20get%20a%20rise%20in%20private%20sector%20confidence.%20Consumer%20and%20business%20confidence%2C%20I%20think%2C%20is%20going%20to%20start%20to%20lift%20as%20well%2C%20much%20like%20the%20feel%20of%20a%20brand%20new%20bull%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Paulsen%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20these%20conditions%20typically%20precede%20a%20broad-based%20rally%20in%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20rising%20stock%20market%20into%202025%20coincides%20with%20Paulsen's%20bullish%20view%20on%20the%20economy%2C%20as%20he%20doesn't%20see%20a%20recession%20happening%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaulsen%20pointed%20to%20strong%20consumer%20and%20business%20balance%20sheets%20and%20%246%20trillion%20in%20money%20market%20funds%20as%20reasons%20for%20his%20optimism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20hard%20for%20a%20recession%20to%20find%20something%20to%20bite%20on%2C%20a%20vulnerability%20to%20bring%20us%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Paulsen%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20when%20pessimism%20is%20still%20very%20elevated%2C%20that%20is%2C%20confidence%20is%20very%20low%2C%20it%20tells%20me%20that%20people%20have%20been%20pretty%20conservative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20Paulsen%20said%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20whether%20the%20Fed%20cuts%20interest%20rates%20by%2025%20or%2050%20basis%20points%20at%20its%20September%20FOMC%20meeting%3B%20all%20that%20matters%20is%20that%20officials%20will%20be%20cutting%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20isn't%20just%20about%20the%20Fed%20doing%2025%20or%2050%2C%20it's%20the%20intention%20to%20ease%20monetary%20policy%20that's%20opening%20up%20a%20brand%20new%20degree%20of%20support%20for%20stocks%20that%20I%20think%20is%20going%20to%20persist%20well%20into%20next%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Paulsen%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-bull-rally-fed-rate-cuts-recession-forecast-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724699237000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7ba756080194819f98b0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-bull-rally-fed-rate-cuts-recession-forecast-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20think%