ndustry%20intensified%20on%20Monday%20as%20a%20case%20was%20charged%20against%20well-known%20filmmaker%20Ranjith%2C%20and%20several%20female%20actors%20stepped%20forward%20with%20disturbing%20accounts%20of%20the%20mistreatment%20they%20faced%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20their%20various%20male%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20charged%20against%20Ranjith%20after%20a%20Bengali%20actress%20filed%20a%20complaint%20on%20Monday%20with%20the%20Kochi%20City%20Police%20Commissioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%2C%20sent%20via%20email%2C%20alleged%20that%20Ranjith%20had%20touched%20her%20inappropriately%20with%20sexual%20intent%20after%20inviting%20her%20to%20act%20in%20the%20movie%20Paleri%20Manikyam%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKochi%20Police%20Commissioner%20S%20Syamsundar%20said%20a%20case%20under%20IPC%20Section%20354%20(assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20on%20a%20woman%20with%20intent%20to%20outrage%20her%20modesty)%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20Ranjith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20actress%2C%20Minu%20Muneer%2C%20who%20has%20appeared%20in%20a%20few%20movies%2C%20levelled%20sexual%20abuse%20allegations%20against%20prominent%20actors%20M%20Mukesh%2C%20who%20is%20also%20an%20MLA%2C%20Jayasurya%20and%20Maniyanpilla%20Raju%2C%20as%20well%20as%20small-time%20actor%20Idavela%20Babu%20who%20has%20a%20prominent%20role%20in%20the%20actors'%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20more%20well-known%20actress%20from%20the%201990s%20also%20came%20forward%20on%20Monday%20with%20allegations%20of%20misconduct%20from%20years%20ago%20against%20a%20noted%20filmmaker.%20She%20has%20expressed%20willingness%20to%20provide%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20filmmaker%20has%20denied%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20Minu%20Muneer%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20writing%20to%20report%20a%20series%20of%20incidents%20of%20physical%20and%20verbal%20abuse%20I%20suffered%20at%20the%20hands%20of%201%20Mukesh%202%20Maniyan%20Pilla%20Raju%2C%203%20Idavela%20Babu%2C%204%20Jayasoorya%20(Jayasurya)%2C%205%20adv%20Chandrasekaran%2C%206%20production%20controller%20Noble%20and%20Vichu%2C%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIn%202013%2C%20I%20was%20subjected%20to%20physical%20and%20verbal%20abuse%20by%20these%20individuals%20while%20working%20on%20a%20project.%20I%20tried%20to%20cooperate%20and%20continue%20working%2C%20but%20the%20abuse%20became%20unbearable%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20actress%2C%20who%20signed%20as%20Minu%20Kurian%20in%20her%20Facebook%20post%2C%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20exception%20of%20Maniyanpilla%20Raju%2C%20none%20of%20the%20actors%20have%20reacted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20same%20day%2C%20a%20junior%20artist%20accused%20actor%20Baburaj%2C%20known%20for%20villain%20roles%2C%20of%20sexual%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERejecting%20the%20allegations%2C%20Baburaj%2C%20an%20office%20bearer%20in%20the%20Association%20of%20Malayalam%20Movie%20Artists%20(A.M.M.A)%2C%20claimed%20it%20was%20an%20attempt%20by%20vested%20interests%20in%20the%20film%20industry%20to%20prevent%20him%20from%20becoming%20A.M.M.A%20general%20secretary%2C%20replacing%20Siddique%2C%20who%20resigned%20on%20Sunday%20amid%20similar%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20serious%20and%20elaborate%20revelations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20charges%20against%20two-time%20CPI(M)%20legislator%20M%20Mukesh%20brought%20embarrassment%20to%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20opposition%20parties%20have%20accused%20the%20Left%20government%20of%20protecting%20the%20predators%2C%20its%20leaders%20put%20up%20a%20defence%2C%20saying%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20has%20been%20formed%20to%20probe%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20the%20continuing%20charges%20against%20Mukesh%2C%20who%20represents%20Kollam%20constituency%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20have%20put%20the%20CPI%20(M)-led%20government%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20harassment%20allegation%20levelled%20by%20a%20woman%20against%20Mukesh%20years%20ago%20also%20resurfaced%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20Minu%20Muneer's%20allegations%20against%20Mukesh%20on%20Monday%2C%20workers%20from%20Yuva%20Morcha%20and%20Mahila%20Congress%20organised%20separate%20marches%20towards%20his%20residence%20in%20Kollam%2C%20demanding%20that%20a%20case%20be%20registered%20against%20him%20and%20that%20he%20resign%20as%20a%20legislator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20leader%20V%20D%20Satheesan%20said%20he%20expects%20that%2C%20like%20Ranjith%20and%20Siddique%2C%20Mukesh%20will%20also%20step%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20revelations%20against%20Mukesh%2C%20Higher%20Education%20Minister%20R%20Bindhu%20said%20any%20accusation%20against%20any%20person%20should%20be%20examined%20on%20factual%20grounds.%20%26quot%3BThe%20wrongdoers%20should%20be%20punished.%20Innocent%20people%20should%20not%20be%20penalised%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20media%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEminent%20writer%20Sara%20Joseph%20and%20Kerala%20Chalachitra%20Academy%20Vice-Chairman%20Premkumar%20raised%20objections%20against%20the%20reported%20inclusion%20of%20Mukesh%20in%20the%20film%20policy%20committee%20of%20the%20upcoming%20cinema%20conclave%20of%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20inclusion%20of%20Mukesh%20on%20the%20panel%20is%20ridiculous.%20He%20should%20resign%20as%20MLA%20if%20he%20has%20any%20self-pride%2C%26quot%3B%20Joseph%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh%20has%20claimed%20he%20is%20being%20deliberately%20targeted%20by%20vested%20interests%20as%20he%20is%20a%20CPI(M)%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20female%20actor%20who%20accused%20him%20has%20also%20levelled%20sexual%20abuse%20allegations%20against%20three%20other%20prominent%20Malayalam%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor%20Maniyanpilla%20Raju%20has%20called%20for%20an%20overall%20investigation.%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20will%20try%20to%20capitalise%20on%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20opined.%20%26quot%3BAmong%20those%20accused%2C%20there%20will%20be%20both%20innocent%20and%20guilty%20parties.%20Therefore%2C%20a%20comprehensive%20investigation%20is%20necessary.%26quot%3B%20Meanwhile%2C%20leading%20actor%20Prithviraj%20has%20called%20for%20corrective%20actions%20from%20A.M.M.A%20and%20a%20comprehensive%20investigation%20into%20the%20various%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20came%20a%20day%20after%20director%20Ranjith%20and%20actor%20Siddique%20stepped%20down%20from%20their%20leadership%20roles%20in%20the%20Kerala%20Chalachitra%20Academy%20and%20A.M.M.A%20respectively%2C%20following%20sexual%20abuse%20allegations%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20mounting%20pressure%20on%20the%20government%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20on%20Sunday%20announced%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20seven-member%20special%20investigation%20team%20for%20the%20probe%20into%20the%20allegations%20made%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Hema%20Committee%20report%20being%20published.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20however%20no%20move%20to%20conduct%20investigations%20on%20revelations%20made%20by%20women%20victims%20in%20the%20Hema%20Committee%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20by%20the%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%2C%20constituted%20by%20the%20Kerala%20government%20after%20the%202017%20actress%20assault%20case%20has%20revealed%20instances%20of%20harassment%20and%20exploitation%20of%20women%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20cinema%20industry%2C%20prompting%20calls%20for%20action%20against%20the%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724698260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fi38q2ao_actor-ranjith_625x300_26_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcase-charged-against-filmmaker-ranjith-after-fresh-sexual-abuse-allegations-6424381%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fallout%20from%20the%20Justice%20K%20Hema%20Committee%20report%20on%20harassment%20and%20abuse%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20intensified%20on%20Monday%20as%20a%20case%20was%20charged%20against%20well-known%20filmmaker%20Ranjith.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20is%20Telegram%20and%20why%20did%20France%20just%20arrest%20its%20CEO%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pavel%20Durov%2C%20CEO%20and%20co-founder%20of%20Telegram%2C%20onstage%20at%20a%20U.S.%20tech%20conference%20in%202015%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccb9b443b5e59d16b53207%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22681%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrench%20authorities%20arrested%20Telegram%20CEO%20Pavel%20Durov%2C%20seen%20here%20in%202015.%3Cp%3ESteve%20Jennings%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20you're%20American%2C%20you%20may%20not%20have%20heard%20of%2C%20or%20used%2C%20Telegram.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20though%2C%20the%20just-about-anything-goes%20messaging%20app%20is%20a%20big%20deal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhich%20is%20why%20the%20arrest%20of%20its%20founder%2C%20and%20the%20questions%20that%20raises%2C%20is%20a%20big%20deal%2C%20too.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFrench%20police%20arrested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpavel-durov-telegram-billionaire-russia-instagram-wealth-founder-dubai-lifestyle-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETelegram%20CEO%20Pavel%20Durov%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20weekend.%20The%20move%20generated%20alarm%20among%20the%20services'%20900%20million%20users%20around%20the%20world