t%20the%20war%20that%20began%20in%20early%202022%2C%C2%A0even%20though%20much%20of%20what%20appears%20there%20about%20the%20conflict%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.atlanticcouncil.org%2Fblogs%2Fnew-atlanticist%2Fukrainian-lawmakers-are-debating-banning-telegram-heres-what-to-know%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Ukrainian%2520government%2520fears%2520the%2Cto%2520find%2520a%2520middle%2520ground.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edubious%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Usage%20of%20the%20app%20has%20skyrocketed%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F2024-08-01%2Fty-article-magazine%2F.premium%2Ffake-news-in-real-time-how-israeli-telegram-channels-took-over-the-news%2F00000191-090f-d4cf-afb5-4ddfc89c0000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIsrael%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Ftelegram-hamas-israel-conflict%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20October%207%20attacks%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERioters%20in%20the%20UK%20used%20Telegram%20to%20communicate%20with%20each%20other%20this%20month%2C%20though%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fneilwilby.com%2F2024%2F03%2F20%2Ftech-giants-block-access-to-tommy-robinsons-telegram-channel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETommy%20Robinson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20far-right%20figure%20linked%20to%20the%20violence%2C%20claims%20that%20Apple%20and%20Android%20phones%20cut%20off%20access%20to%20his%20channel%20earlier%20this%20year.%20The%20app%20has%20long%20been%20accused%20of%20serving%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fworld%2F2017%2F6%2F30%2F15886506%2Fterrorism-isis-telegram-social-media-russia-pavel-durov-twitter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterrorists%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fhikvision-cameras-telegram-children%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dfalcon_y0pL%26utm_social-type%3Downed%26mbid%3Dsocial_twitter%26utm_brand%3Dwired%26utm_