0the%20National%20Conference-Congress%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20BJP%20formed%20a%20ruling%20alliance%20with%20the%20PDP%20after%20the%20election%20results%20presented%20a%20hung%20house.%20But%20the%20alliance%20of%20the%20two%20ideologically%20mismatched%20parties%20was%20short-lived%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20came%20under%20President's%20Rule%20in%202018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20surprise%20of%20this%20election%20is%20the%20participation%20of%20the%20candidates%20of%20the%20banned%20Jamaat-e-Islami%2C%20who%20are%20contesting%20as%20Independents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20an%20important%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Abdullah%20said.%20%26quot%3BAn%20organisation%20that%20spent%20the%20last%2030-plus%20years%20telling%20the%20people%20of%20Kashmir%20that%20elections%20are%20'haram'%2C%20that%20they%20should%20not%20participate%20in%20elections%2C%20was%20talking%20about%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20not%20being%20a%20part%20of%20India%2C%20today%20is%20willing%20to%20take%20the%20same%20oath%20on%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20that%20mainstream%20political%20parties%20have%20taken.%20This%20is%20a%20huge%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20his%20own%20decision%20to%20contest%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20getting%20into%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20all%20that...%20Ultimately%2C%20if%20I%20believe%20I%20am%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20National%20Conference%2C%20then%20I%20must%20lead%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20the%20assembly%2C%20he%20said%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bhypocritical%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bseen%20as%20hypocritical%26quot%3B%20if%20he%20were%20to%20tell%20people%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20believe%20in%20this%20assembly%2C%20but%20you%20must%20vote%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot