olice%20Clarifies%20After%20Video%20Shows%20Crowd%20At%20Hospital%20Crime%20Scene%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20hospital's%20seminar%20hall%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20discovery%20of%20the%20August%20rape%20murder%2C%20has%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20procedures%20followed%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20crime%20scene%20preservation.%20The%20video%2C%20which%20is%20being%20widely%20circulated%20online%2C%20appears%20to%20give%20credence%20to%20CBI%20claims%20that%20the%20crime%20scene%20has%20been%20contaminated.%20%C2%A0After%20daylong%20speculation%2C%20the%20police%20responded%2C%20saying%20they%20had%20cordoned%20off%20the%20relevant%20portion%20of%20the%20hall.%20The%20police%20have%20also%20assured%20that%20proper%20procedures%20were%20followed%20to%20preserve%20evidence%20and%20ensure%20a%20thorough%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%2C%20which%20is%20not%20verified%20by%20NDTV%2C%20apparently%20shows%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20seminar%20hall%20where%20the%20partially%20clothed%20body%20of%20the%20young%20doctor%20was%20found%20hours%20before.%20But%20instead%20of%20being%20an%20empty%2C%20cordoned-off%20zone%2C%20it%20was%20teeming%20with%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20said%20several%20people%20close%20to%20then%20Principal%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20including%20his%20lawyer%2C%20were%20also%20seen%20in%20the%2043-second%20clip%20from%20August%209.%20Intermingled%20with%20the%20crowd%20were%20police%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20evening%2C%20a%20police%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20video%20has%20gone%20viral%20showing%20the%20place%20of%20occurrence.%20This%20is%20a%20clarification.%20The%20body%20found%20in%20the%20seminar%20hall%20was%20in%20one%20portion%20of%20the%20seminar%20hall.%2040%20feet%20of%20the%20room%20was%20cordoned%20off.%20The%20video%20is%20outside%20the%20cordoned%20off%20area%20where%20family%20members%2C%20doctors%20and%20the%20police%20were%20present%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnPolice%20officers%20said%20the%20entire%20seminar%20hall%20is%2051%20feet%20x%2032%20feet%2C%20of%20which%2040%20feet%20x%2011%20feet%20was%20cordoned%20off.%20Only%20the%2011-feet%20portion%20is%20shown%20in%20the%20viral%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAuthorised%20persons%2C%20including%2010%20forensic%20teams%20and%20those%20who%20removed%20the%20body%2C%20were%20present%20at%20the%20spot%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20state%20General%20Secretary%20Jagannath%20Chattopadhyay%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20so%20many%20people%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20crime%20can%20easily%20compromise%20evidence.%20He%20also%20alleged%20that%20this%20could%20have%20been%20done%20deliberately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20high%20possibility%20of%20tampering%20with%20evidence.%20Those%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20tampering%20and%20for%20the%20loss%20of%20evidence%20are%20equally%20guilty%20and%20they%20should%20be%20arrested%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20has%20surfaced%20more%20than%20a%20week%20after%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20case%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20following%20an%20order%20by%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court.%20The%20central%20agency%2C%20after%20its%20initial%20investigation%2C%20had%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20by%20the%20time%20they%20took%20over%20the%20case%2C%20%26quot%3Beverything%20was%20altered%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20too%2C%20found%20anomalies%20and%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20timeline%20recorded%20by%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%2C%20raising%20serious%20questions%20about%20the%20handling%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%209%2C%20the%20second-year%20postgrad%20had%20gone%20to%20an%20empty%20seminar%20room%20alone%20after%20a%2036-ho