over%20attempted%20pregnancies.%20The%20social%20worker%20was%20quick%20to%20deduce%20that%20this%20girl%20had%20been%20married%20at%20the%20age%20of%2014%20in%20a%20blatant%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330387%2Fias-officer-district-magistrate-saju-vaheed-balika-manch-prevent-child-marriage-south-tripura%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecase%20of%20child%20marriage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20shocking%20to%20him.%20But%20what%20the%20medic%20said%20next%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20just%20one%20of%20many%20such%20cases%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20compelled%20Kamble%20to%20dedicate%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20life%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20stopping%20child%20marriages%20in%20Beed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20this%2C%20he%20says%20that%20while%20a%20majority%20of%20such%20cases%20were%20bracketed%20as%20%E2%80%98maternal%20deaths%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20real%20cause%20of%20death%20is%20child%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamble%20was%20joined%20by%20Ashok%20Tangde%20(55)%20in%20his%20quest%20to%20put%20a%20halt%20to%20this%20widespread%20practice.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20(CWC)%20%E2%80%94%20an%20autonomous%20institution%20formed%20under%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act%20(2015)%20%E2%80%94%20the%20duo%20has%20been%20working%20to%20ensure%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346951%2Fassam-pallabi-ghosh-impact-and-dialogue-foundation-child-human-trafficking-rehabilitation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafer%20world%20for%20girls%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Beed%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchild-marriage-1724157436.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20a