se%20expanses%20of%20green%20attracted%20the%20children%2C%20making%20them%20regular%20visitors%20at%20the%20site.%20As%20luck%20would%20have%20it%2C%20the%20person%20conducting%20these%20tree%20plantations%20was%20a%20teacher%20by%20the%20name%20of%20Angshuman%20Thakur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoticing%20the%20trend%20of%20school%20dropouts%20and%20seeing%20the%20children%20accompany%20their%20parents%20to%20work%20deeply%20moved%20the%2040-year-old.%20Since%20their%20schools%20provided%20mid-day%20meals%20to%20children%2C%20Angshuman%20first%20started%20providing%20the%20same%20to%20a%20group%20of%20five.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20meals%2C%20he%20also%20served%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espoonfuls%20of%20knowledge%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethrough%20his%20open%20air%20classes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20alumna%20of%20Visva%20Bharati%20University%20in%20Santikentan%2C%20he%20imbibed%20the%20principles%20of%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20by%20providing%20a%20holistic%20education%20in%20sync%20with%20nature%2C%20which%20goes%20beyond%20merely%20words%20written%20in%20textbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20with%20five%20children%20in%202021%2C%20today%20over%20105%20children%20study%20at%20Angshuman%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Anirvana%20Gacher%20Iskul%E2%80%99%20(Anirvana%20means%20inextinguishable%20and%20Gach%20means%20tree).%20Running%20on%20the%20benevolence%20of%20kind%20strangers%20and%20his%20own%20savings%2C%20it%20costs%20Rs%20300%20per%20month%20to%20educate%20a%20child%20in%20this%20school%20under%20a%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELearning%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAngshuman%20works%20as%20a%20Bengali%20literature%20professor%20at%20Prof%20Syed%20Nurul%20Has