.%20Today%2C%20he%20runs%20RampMyCity%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20works%20to%20improve%20accessibility%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%20and%20the%20elderly%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20adapted%20to%20his%20new%20reality%20back%20then%2C%20he%20knew%20that%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20let%20his%20wheelchair%20stop%20him%20from%20living%20fully.%20Although%20public%20attitudes%20towards%20him%20changed%2C%20with%20some%20friends%20offering%20him%20sympathy%20while%20others%20becoming%20distant%2C%20he%20committed%20himself%20to%20strenuous%20physical%20therapy%20during%20the%20first%20four%20years%20after%20the%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConfronted%20with%20complications%20such%20as%20bladder%20issues%20and%20muscle%20atrophy%20from%20his%20spinal%20cord%20injury%2C%20Prateek%20chose%20to%20focus%20on%20his%20progress%20over%20dwelling%20on%20the%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20of%20physical%20training%20helped%20Prateek%20make%20significant%20progress%2C%20but%20he%20faced%20a%20new%20problem%3A%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20go%20out%20to%20eat%20at%20his%20favourite%20restaurants%20or%20any%20other%20places%20he%20enjoyed%20before.%20This%20led%20him%20to%20create%20his%20startup%20as%20he%20understood%20just%20how%20crucial%20ramps%20were%20in%20breaking%20barriers%20and%20accessing%20the%20world%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202020%2C%20RampMyCity%20aims%20to%20provide%20complete%20infrastructure%20solutions%20for%20both%20public%20and%20private%20sectors.%20This%20includes%20ramps%2C%20accessibility%20audits%2C%20retrofitting%2C%20and%20more.%20So%20far%2C%20Prateek%20has%20helped%20install%20over%20530%20ramps%20in%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Goa%2C%20Gurgaon%2C%20and%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup