%20a%20champion%20swimmer%20at%20the%20school%20and%20district%20levels.%20However%2C%20after%20Class%209%2C%20swimming%20took%20a%20backseat%20as%20her%20studies%20became%20the%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%2018%20years%2C%20education%2C%20business%2C%20marriage%2C%20and%20raising%20kids%20took%20precedence%2C%20and%20her%20sport%20faded%20into%20the%20background.%20As%20a%20young%20mother%2C%20she%20juggled%20these%20roles%20while%20longing%20for%20the%20determined%20young%20girl%20who%20once%20embraced%20every%20challenge.%20The%20demands%20of%20everyday%20life%20%E2%80%94%20managing%20a%20resort%20in%20Nashik%2C%20and%20being%20a%20mother%2C%20wife%2C%20and%20daughter%20%E2%80%94%20began%20to%20take%20their%20toll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20she%20lost%20herself%2C%20along%20with%20the%20fearless%20young%20girl%20who%20was%20up%20for%20any%20challenge%2C%20she%20wondered%3F%20This%20search%20for%20self-love%20led%20her%20back%20to%20her%20first%20love%3A%20water.%20One%20might%20think%20she%20would%20simply%20return%20to%20swimming%2C%20but%20Tanvi%20had%20loftier%20dreams.%20Instead%20of%20just%20diving%20back%20into%20the%20pool%2C%20she%20set%20herself%20a%20Herculean%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202022%2C%20over%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%2C%20she%20confided%20in%20her%20husband%20about%20her%20wish%20to%20fulfil%20one%20of%20her%20childhood%20dreams%20%E2%80%94%20to%20swim%20the%20English%20Channel%2C%20a%20daunting%20long-distance%20challenge%20spanning%20over%2033%20km%20from%20England%20to%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20dream%20had%20taken%20root%20when%20she%20was%20just%20a%20child%2C%20inspired%20by%20an%20article%20she%20read%20about%20a%20swimmer%20who%20had%20accomplished%20this%20incredible%20feat.%20Even%20before%20setting%20foot%20in%20a%20pool%2C%20the%2033-year-old%20took%20a%20bold%20step%20and%20registered%20herself%20for%20the%20swim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3