%99s%20stopping%20you%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20Tanvi%20Deore%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723816133000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D361675%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nashik-based%20Tanvi%20Deore%20(33)%20rekindled%20her%20passion%20for%20swimming%20after%20an%2018-year%20hiatus%20to%20fulfil%20her%20childhood%20dream%20of%20swimming%20the%20English%20Channel.%20Despite%20facing%20physical%2C%20mental%2C%20and%20logistical%20challenges%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20how%20she%20successfully%20completed%20the%2033-kilometre%20swim.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F361675%2Fnashik-swimmer-tanvi-deore-swam-across-english-channel-dover-france-open-water-swimming-champion%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20World%20Beyond%20Concrete%3A%205%20Construction%20Materials%20India%20is%20Using%20to%20Make%20Sustainable%20Homes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMud%20is%20%3Cem%3Ekaccha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(raw).%E2%80%9D%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSustainable%20architecture%20isn%E2%80%99t%20pretty.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchitect%20Guruprasad%20Rane%20of%20the%20firm%20%E2%80%98Bhoomija%E2%80%99%20in%20Kerala%20would%20often%20hear%20some%20of%20these%20opinions%20being%20shared%20by%20his%20clients%20who%20wanted%20a%20new%20space%20built%20for%20them.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20now%20that%20is%20slowly%20changing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClients%20these%20days%20are%20open%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F224900%2Fmumbai-architect-sustainable-homes-solar-air-conditioning-ec